'''第17太陽週期'''是從1755年開始紀錄太陽黑子以來的第17[[太陽週期|太陽週期]]<ref name="Kane">Kane, R.P. (2002). "[http://www.springerlink.com/content/qtq52nl8vtq7w2t6/ Some Implications Using the Group Sunspot Number Reconstruction] {{Webarchive|url=https://archive.is/20121204174904/http://www.springerlink.com/content/qtq52nl8vtq7w2t6/ |date=2012-12-04 }}". ''Solar Physics'' '''205(2)''', 383-401.</ref><ref name=SpaceToday>{{cite web | title=The Sun: Did You Say the Sun Has Spots? | url=http://www.spacetoday.org/SolSys/Sun/Sunspots.html | publisher=Space Today Online | accessdate=12 August 2010 | archive-date=2017-07-22 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170722010544/http://www.spacetoday.org/SolSys/Sun/Sunspots.html | dead-url=no }}</ref>。這個週期開始於1933年9月，結束於1944年2月，持續了10.4年。最大平滑黑子數（超過12個月期間的黑子月平均數值）為119.2（1937年4月），最小的數值為7.7<ref name="SIDC Monthly Smoothed Sunspot Number">SIDC Monthly Smoothed Sunspot Number. "[http://sidc.oma.be/sunspot-data/] {{Wayback|url=http://sidc.oma.be/sunspot-data/ |date=20140328111426 }}"</ref>，在這個週期內總共約有269天沒有黑子<ref name="Spotless Days">Spotless Days. "[http://spaceweather.com/glossary/spotlessdays.htm?PHPSESSID=dli444kmrjgre0rjq6l86fv144] {{Wayback|url=http://spaceweather.com/glossary/spotlessdays.htm?PHPSESSID=dli444kmrjgre0rjq6l86fv144 |date=20160303185014 }}"</ref><ref name="What's Wrong with the Sun? (Nothing)">What's Wrong with the Sun? (Nothing) more information: Spotless Days. "[http://science.nasa.gov/headlines/y2008/11jul_solarcycleupdate.htm] {{Wayback|url=http://science.nasa.gov/headlines/y2008/11jul_solarcycleupdate.htm |date=20080714032353 }}"</ref><ref name="Solaemon's Spotless Days Page">Solaemon's Spotless Days Page. "[http://users.telenet.be/j.janssens/Spotless/Spotless.html] {{Wayback|url=http://users.telenet.be/j.janssens/Spotless/Spotless.html |date=20170722234836 }}"</ref>。1938年1月5日的宏偉極光遍布歐洲各地，遠在南方的葡萄牙和西西里都能看見，使許多人受到驚嚇。有些人認為紅色的光表示大火，而有些人聯想到[[法蒂瑪聖母|法蒂瑪預言]]。在1940年4月3日的極光在紐約能看見<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.solarstorms.org/SRefStorms.html |title=存档副本 |access-date=2016-09-22 |archive-date=2011-08-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110816003232/http://www.solarstorms.org/SRefStorms.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

